<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-03 13:04 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4270 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r f BC-EXAMINER-SALE-HNS &LR;      05-03 0786
