<P>
   &UR; JUST HOW `COMPASSIONATE' IS GEORGE W.? &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; BUSH-BLEEDING-HEART-ECONOMIST-850&AMP;add &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (UNDATED) _ Just how compassionate can a Republican get before
he has to leave the GOP and join Vegans for Global Justice? George
W. Bush seems bent on finding out. One moment he is holding a
get-to-know-you meeting with a bunch of gay Republicans. The next
he is holding forth on education or the environment or some other
squishy-squashy crowd-pleaser. It is enough to make a red-blooded
conservative choke on his spotted-oil drumstick. &QL;
</P>
