<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-03 16:39 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4469 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a BC-CPT-ECOMMERCE-COLUMN-     05-03 1385
</HEADER>
