Cox News Service, at 404-526-5456.
</P>
<P>
   AIRLINES-LIVETV _ A couple of small airlines are offering live
TV on flights _ so passengers don't have to miss an episode of
their favorite sitcoms. We'll look at how fast this is likely to
spread to the big guys, plus other technologocial advances in the
pipeline _Internet hook-ups, movies on demand while you fly.
(Thurston, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 25.
</P>
