   SONATURAL-GAS _ El Paso Energy Corp. plans to add 73 miles to
its Southern Natural interstate natural gas pipeline to carry more
gas to Georgia Power Co. and other Southeastern utilities tat are
growing more dependent on that fuel. (Quinn, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 6.
