<P>
   VIEQUES-HONEYMOON _ VIEQUES, Puerto Rico _ Bob and Andrea
Bartels, of Austin, Texas _ and formerly of Atlanta _ wanted a
special honeymoon away from it all. They chose this pristine little
island ``because it's an isolated getaway,'' with no televisions
and few telephones. They never dreamed three months ago, when they
made the reservations, that a showdown between protesters and
federal agents could spoil the moment. Developing. (MWilliams, Cox
