his works at the Church of St. Ignatius Loyolain in New York on
Thursday. The performers include the Tallis Scholars; the Flux
Ensemble; the Juilliard Brass Ensemble; Patricia Rozario, a soprano
who has recorded several of his vocal works; and Sir Paul
McCartney, who has known Taverner since 1970, when the Beatles'
