wondering if their honeymoon might be interupted by federal agents
and U.S. Marines out to end the bombing range protest on the tiny
island. Married on Sunday in Montgomery, Ala., the couple arrived
on Vieques Monday, just as a showdown appeared imminent. ``I found
out when we got to the San Juan airport,'' says, Andrea. ``He
showed me a newspaper and I said, 'Oh my God, we're going to a war
